Chinchou (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0169: Crobat
Pokémon
#0171: Lanturn →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Chinchou (TCG Pocket).

Chinchou has been featured on 26 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Genesis expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Chinchou cards are normally Lightning-type or Water-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Chinchou

Chinchou
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
